{"tid":82932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港出發】貨機在吉爾吉斯撞民居 增至32人死","createTime":"2017-01-16T10:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T10:41:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4c8d40b71533c0a9e0f8a24bf46be8abde3f83","tid":82932,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170116/large/1484539130_ad07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2Flarge%2F1484539130_ad07.jpg&h=6530c25e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【香港時間12:32】官方指增至32人死 <br />\n<br />\n土耳其航空一架從香港起飛的貨機周一在中亞國家吉爾吉斯（Kyrgyzstan）發生空難，貨機在馬納斯國際機場（Manas International Airport）附近撞民居，死亡人數增至至少32人。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170116/large/1484537488_9a87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2Flarge%2F1484537488_9a87.jpg&h=fc8237c3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出事貨機機種為波音747，編號為TK6491，事發地點距離機場跑道只有數百米。吉爾吉斯政府表示空難造成32人死亡。衞生部早前指死亡人數為16人，救援人員已找到一名機師，以及15名當地居民的屍體，其中6人是小孩。 <br />\n<br />\n現場照片可見，貨機在民居墜落後發生大火，消防趕到現場撲滅火勢，但多幢大廈被撞毀，受損範圍廣泛，至少15幢大樓受影響。 <br />\n<br />\n目前未清楚事發時機上有多少人，一架波音747通常可以載至少兩名機組人員。土耳其航空暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\nbnonews/路透社 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/photo/bknint-20170116111211912-0116_17011_001_04b.jpg?20170116123421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170116%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170116111211912-0116_17011_001_04b.jpg%3F20170116123421&h=9cf0add8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/photo/bknint-20170116111211912-0116_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170116123421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170116%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170116111211912-0116_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170116123421&h=98370305&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/photo/bknint-20170116111211912-0116_17011_001_03b.jpg?20170116123421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170116%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170116111211912-0116_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20170116123421&h=ade89aaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0088fcc55b3b18805ad2eba10cbb4d7cc0d2ee56","tid":82932,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"Hkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0eaa68f117d26efbac6cef02f238add4f0c341","tid":82932,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"空難最慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f738e4d7a6443d4cec341d8be0ebce403e9a5f48","tid":82932,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"土耳其會唔會嬲鳩香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}